The FM-10G-DA-1M-01 consists of two 10G SFP+ modules and an attached 1M (3.3ft) copper cable. The FM-10G-DA-1M provides an easy way to directly connect two switches on the same rack at speeds of up to 10Gbps.

The Pakedge FM-10G-LR is a 10G fibre module designed to bring 10Gbps switch-to-switch fibre connectivity to any switch with an SFP+ port. When used with Pakedge Single Mode Fibre Cable, it provides guaranteed stable and consistent network performance with no loss of speed or throughput.

The Pakedge FM-1G-SM is a 1G a 1000BASE-LX fibre module designed to bring 1Gbps switch-to-switch fibre connectivity to any switch with an SFP port. The fibre module supports single mode and 1000BASE-LX as outlined in the IEEE standard 802.3 specifications for 1000BASE-LX. When used with Pakedge fibre cable, the Pakedge FM-1G-SM provides stable and consistent network performance with no loss of speed or throughput.
